I was just trying out the new replay system with the new client. When I hit exit game this random error message appeared that says 

&quot;We&#039;re attempting to automatically reconnect you to League of Legends. If your internet connection is otherwise ok, check our support page for possible solutions.&quot; 

figured servers are just down for this update, but didn&#039;t know if i was the only one getting this shit or not....
